{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change the legal age for smoking / use of e-cigarettes from 18 to 16",
        "additional_details": "The reason why I want the legal age for smoking / use of e-cigarettes to change from 18 to 16 is because people aged 16 and 17 are \u2018Young Adults\u2019, and should be able to smoke.\r\n\r\nAlso, e-cigarettes are less harmful than normal cigarettes and it would be better for those who originally started smoking at a young age to turn to e-cigarettes to help them quit.\r\n\r\nAs the age of consent in the UK is 16, In my opinion I think the legal age to purchase/use tobacco, cigarettes and e-cigarettes should be 16.",
        "background": "Change the rule about smoking/use of e-cigarettes. Change the legal age to purchase tobacco, cigarettes and e-cigarettes from 18 to 16 and the legal smoking age from 18 to 16.",
